/span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">可以视为质点</span></p><p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:6pt; text-align:justify; line-height:150%; widows:0; orphans:0; font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">B. </span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">加油过程中，运油—</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">的惯性越来越大</span></p><p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:6pt; text-align:justify; line-height:150%; widows:0; orphans:0; font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">C. </span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">以运油—</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">为参考系，歼</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">-10</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">、歼</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">-20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">战机是运动的</span></p><p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:6pt; text-align:justify; line-height:150%; widows:0; orphans:0; font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">D. </span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">以歼</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">-10</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">战机为参考系，运油</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">-20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">和歼</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">-20</span><span style="font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">都是静止的</span></p><p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:6pt; text-align:justify; line-height:150%; widows:0; orphans:0; font-size:10.5pt"><img src="./aul55-asi8q_files/aul55-asi8q.048.png" width="167" height="98" alt="学科网(www.zxxk.com)--教育资源门户，提供试题试卷、教案、课件、教学论文、素材等各类教学资源库下载，还有大量丰富的教学资讯！" style="-aw-left-pos:0pt; -aw-rel-hpos:column; -aw-rel-vpos:paragraph; -aw-top-pos:0pt; -aw-wrap-